---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Travel Expenses App | Julius Bruch"
    description="Case Study: Travel Expenses App. Automated travel expense approval workflow with integrated PDF report generation for fast and compliant accounting."
>
    <main>
        <!-- Project Detail Section -->
        <section class="project-detail">
            <div class="container">
                <a href="/#projects" class="back-link">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
                    <span data-en="Back to Projects" data-de="Zurück zu Projekte">Back to Projects</span>
                </a>

                <div class="project-detail-content">
                    <div class="project-detail-header">
                        <h1 data-en="Travel Expenses App" data-de="Reisekosten App">Travel Expenses App</h1>
                        <p class="project-category" data-en="Power Apps | Power Automate | PDF Generation" data-de="Power Apps | Power Automate | PDF-Generierung">Power Apps | Power Automate | PDF Generation</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="project-detail-image">
                        <div class="image-placeholder" aria-hidden="true">✈️</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="project-detail-body">
                        <h2 data-en="Project Overview" data-de="Projektübersicht">Project Overview</h2>
                        <p data-en="Automated travel expense approval workflow with integrated PDF report generation for fast and compliant accounting." data-de="Automatisierter Genehmigungs-Workflow für Reisekosten mit integrierter PDF-Berichterstellung für eine schnelle und rechtskonforme Buchhaltung.">Automated travel expense approval workflow with integrated PDF report generation for fast and compliant accounting.</p>

                        <h2 data-en="Key Features" data-de="Hauptfunktionen">Key Features</h2>
                        <ul class="features-list">
                            <li data-en="Submission of travel expenses with receipt attachments" data-de="Einreichung von Reisekosten mit Beleg-Anhängen">Submission of travel expenses with receipt attachments</li>
                            <li data-en="Direct supervisor approval workflow" data-de="Direkter Genehmigungsworkflow durch Vorgesetzte">Direct supervisor approval workflow</li>
                            <li data-en="Automated PDF report generation via Power Automate" data-de="Automatisierte PDF-Berichterstellung via Power Automate">Automated PDF report generation via Power Automate</li>
                            <li data-en="Integration with SharePoint for data and file storage" data-de="Integration mit SharePoint für Daten- und Dateispeicherung">Integration with SharePoint for data and file storage</li>
                            <li data-en="Mobile-friendly interface for on-the-go expense tracking" data-de="Mobilfreundliche Oberfläche für die Spesenerfassung unterwegs">Mobile-friendly interface for on-the-go expense tracking</li>
                            <li data-en="Email notifications for status updates" data-de="E-Mail-Benachrichtigungen für Status-Updates">Email notifications for status updates</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h2 data-en="Technologies Used" data-de="Verwendete Technologien">Technologies Used</h2>
                        <div class="tech-tags">
                            <span class="tech-tag">Power Apps</span>
                            <span class="tech-tag">SharePoint</span>
                            <span class="tech-tag">Power Automate</span>
                            <span class="tech-tag">Microsoft 365</span>
                        </div>

                        <h2 data-en="Results" data-de="Ergebnisse">Results</h2>
                        <p data-en="The implementation completely eliminated manual paperwork and accelerated the approval process. Accounting now receives standardized, perfectly formatted PDF reports, drastically reducing processing time and manual errors." data-de="Die Implementierung hat manuellen Papierkram vollständig elimininiert und den Genehmigungsprozess beschleunigt. Die Buchhaltung erhält nun standardisierte, perfekt formatierte PDF-Berichte, was die Bearbeitungszeit und manuelle Fehler drastisch reduziert.">The implementation completely eliminated manual paperwork and accelerated the approval process. Accounting now receives standardized, perfectly formatted PDF reports, drastically reducing processing time and manual errors.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact CTA -->
        <section class="contact-cta">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 data-en="Interested in a similar solution?" data-de="Interessiert an einer ähnlichen Lösung?">Interested in a similar solution?</h2>
                <p data-en="Let's discuss how I can help your organization streamline processes and boost productivity." data-de="Lassen Sie uns besprechen, wie ich Ihrer Organisation helfen kann, Prozesse zu optimieren und die Produktivität zu erhöhen.">Let's discuss how I can help your organization streamline processes and boost productivity.</p>
                <a href="/#contact" class="cta-button" data-en="Get in Touch" data-de="Kontaktieren Sie mich">Get in Touch</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>